{"tid":1988779,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[玄學撚]金仔真係出左事？定大步檻過？","createTime":"2020-04-25T12:20:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-25T12:21:23.000Z","uid":203889,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a53d21d16df4af0757fb1056cbfd6db5fd50e5a9","tid":1988779,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T12:20:30.000Z","msg":"利申本人尚在學習階段，可能會唔準<br />\n如果燈左，還請大家屌輕力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小弟試用易占測試，頭先嘗試起卦，得到<br />\n<br />\n天雷無妄 上九爻變 澤雷隨 伏卦 澤天夬<br />\n<br />\n天雷無妄 上九爻：<br />\n上九，无妄行，有眚，无攸利。<br />\n《象》曰：无妄之行，窮之災也。<br />\n意料之外的行程，有災難，無所利。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><em>（爻辭source: <a href=\"https://www.eee-learning.com/book/neweee25）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eee-learning.com%2Fbook%2Fneweee25%EF%BC%89&d=5PHCsmqc8bXRSfVPwy6hKtT2hWdA4JmoO%2FtHFZtOkv0%3D&h=c724460e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.eee-learning.com/book/neweee25）</a></em></span><br />\n有意料之外的災難臨到金仔身上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇卦象<br />\n天為乾，乾為人，<br />\n爻變為澤，<br />\n澤為兌，兌為毀折，<br />\n即係「一個人毀壞了」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n伏卦澤天夬<br />\n澤天夬大象為兌，亦是毀折之意<br />\n<br />\n然後變卦澤雷隨卦辭：<br />\n《象》曰：澤中有雷，隨。君子以嚮晦入宴息。<br />\n<br />\n真係幾符合植物人訓係度唔郁得嘅描述<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n估計佢真係植物人左，半年內有生命危險<br />\n<br />\n有其他想法嘅歡迎一齊討論"},{"pid":"87fa6fc3e3e843a6472643943765f9e123b0c310","tid":1988779,"uid":203889,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T12:21:23.000Z","msg":"開錯台，去神秘台重開<br />\n勿覆"}]}